    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"276656\">@Valeria de Paiva</span>  Thanks, this is a great chapter! With this new terminology I can simplify my question to: Is there an account of point-free correspondence theory (for modal logic)?</p>\n<p>This led me to this <a href=\"https://link.springer.com/content/pdf/10.1007/978-3-7091-6510-2_5.pdf\">chapter</a> which gives the most complete account with many examples.</p>",
